          <div data-review id="samsung-bespoke-jet-ai">
            <span data-tag>Premium</span>
            <h2>Samsung Bespoke Jet AI</h2>
            <div data-specs>
              <span><strong>Capacitate:</strong> Rezervor praf 0.5L (aspirator), Rezervor apa 160ml (mop)</span>
